{"tid":1366104,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"幹你娘課爆","createTime":"2019-07-26T00:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:45:47.000Z","uid":55524,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eaadc41c07a4852dc42be824c4f33f2b04c58f3d","tid":1366104,"uid":55524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"我是個打機亦不會課金的人，而我課金的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘課爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘課爆，老子才不管甚麼媒體聯署學生組織的，每次課就是課你全家。獨立媒體課成傳媒龍頭，美國登報課成全球聯署登報。課金求一千課一萬，跟把整個首期的錢全課給你沒兩樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我這個月課足25天，銀行跑來跟我說，這個月存款結餘只餘下二十六元，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"29b1bf5cc43a14e339ec5bf4a748c085b95c4989","tid":1366104,"uid":280424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"有冇多D<br />\n呢種永遠睇唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25dc932144de50af90c4444df510786cdeb92323","tid":1366104,"uid":55524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fe4f6e78e34ae876b95c52a220a11ed90cc311","tid":1366104,"uid":55524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}